Notes: Mrs T Martin (HOD English, Henderson High School, P.O. Box 21141, Henderson, Auckland) says this is used by school kids (13-15 yrs)in West Auckland schools when they are caught red-handed doing something they shouldn't and suggests it comes from the use of speed cameras.
